\displaystyle \lim_{x\to0}  \frac{\sqrt{(x+3)} - \sqrt3} x
\displaystyle \frac{\sqrt{(x+3)} - \sqrt3}x\times\frac{\sqrt{(x+3)} + \sqrt3}{\sqrt{(x+3)} + \sqrt3}
x
\lim_{x \to 0} \frac{\sqrt{x+3}-\sqrt{3}}{x} = \frac{d \sqrt{x}}{dx}|_{x = 3} = \frac{1}{2 \sqrt{3}}
